OL,3,CDeaths of married British couple in
OL,4,CFrance 'treated as murder-suicide'
OL,6,FThe sudden deaths of a married British
OL,7,Fcouple at their home in the south of
OL,8,FFrance are being treated as a murder-
OL,9,Fsuicide.
OL,11,FDawn Kerr, originally from Eyemouth,
OL,12,Fand Andrew Searle, who were both aged
OL,13,Fin their 60s, were found dead in the
OL,14,Fhamlet of Les Pesquies in Villefranche-
OL,15,Fde-Rouergue, Aveyron, on February 6.
OL,17,FMrs Kerr was found lying dead in front
OL,18,Fof her house partly undressed and with
OL,19,Fa significant head injury while Mr
OL,20,FSearle was also found dead inside the
OL,21,Fproperty.
