OL,6,FPolice launched an investigation to
OL,7,Festablish whether the couple died as a
OL,8,Fresult of a murder-suicide or if a
OL,9,Fthird party was involved.
OL,11,FProsecutor Fabrice Belargent said that
OL,12,F"the analysis carried out does not so
OL,13,Ffar show any evidence that a third
OL,14,Fparty was involved".
OL,16,FIt is understood Ms Kerr and Mr Searle
OL,17,Fwere the mother and stepfather of
OL,18,FScottish actor and musician Callum
OL,19,FKerr, who played PC George Kiss in the
OL,20,FChannel 4 soap opera Hollyoaks, and
OL,21,Fappeared in Netflix's Virgin River.
