OL,6,FA statement posted on Mr Kerr's social
OL,7,Fmedia accounts on February 8 said: "At
OL,8,Fthis time, Callum Kerr and Amanda Kerr
OL,9,Fare grieving the loss of their mother,
OL,10,FDawn Searle (nee Smith, Kerr), while
OL,11,FTom Searle and Ella Searle are
OL,12,Fmourning the loss of their father,
OL,13,FAndrew Searle."
OL,15,FIt asked for the family's privacy to
OL,16,Fbe respected "during this difficult
OL,17,Fperiod."
