OL,6,FAccording to his LinkedIn page, Mr
OL,7,FSearle was a retired fraud
OL,8,Finvestigator specialising in financial
OL,9,Fcrime prevention who worked at
OL,10,Fcompanies including Standard Life and
OL,11,FBarclays Bank.
OL,13,FA statement issued by French
OL,14,Fprosecutors in February said: "The two
OL,15,Fdeceased persons, a man and a woman,
OL,16,Fwere the owners of the house in which
OL,17,Ftheir bodies were discovered.
OL,19,F"They were British expatriates,
OL,20,Fretired, and had been living in
OL,21,FAveyron for five years.
